description: Overview* This USB-A to Micro-B SuperSpeed USB 3.0 cable brings significant performance enhancements to the ubiquitous USB standard, while remaining compatible with the billions of USB enabled devices currently deployed in the market.* SuperSpeed USB 3.0 delivers 10x the data transfer rate of Hi-Speed USB 2.0, up to 5Gbps, as well as improved power efficiency.* USB 3.0 utilizes a bi-directional data interface rather than USB 2.0's half-duplex arrangement, where data can only flow in one direction at a time, giving a ten-fold increase in theoretical bandwidth.Specifications* Compatibility: Backward compatible with USB 2.0* Data Transfer Rate: Supports USB 3.0 SuperSpeed up to 5 Gbps* Power Supply: 900 mA* Connector Plating: Gold plated* Cable Shield Type: Foil and braid shielding* Wire Gauge: 28 AWG
title: Cable Matters SuperSpeed USB 3.0 Type A to Micro-B Cable in Blue 6 Feet
